data.description: PRICE REDUCED!! Charming rancher located in the Central area with a yellow front door that welcomes you into the bright, cheery living room and dining area with hardwood floors, and a decorative fireplace. Adorable kitchen with tile floor, stainless gas range and hood, dishwasher, and refrigerator. Two bedrooms with hardwood floors and a full bathroom on the main level. The carpeted recreation room downstairs is a cozy place to gather and watch movies, sit and relax or play games. Bedroom number three, bath, and laundry room complete the basement level. The back yard has a large deck, storage shed, and privacy fence. Attached one car garage. Central air conditioning to help cool off the hot summer days. Call today to schedule your private showing.
